title: Spacious 2x1 Industrial Style W/ Laundry in unit!!
posting_body: Lantern Lofts is a newly constructed 5-story building featuring 20 exciting residences.

Located at 1168 Folsom in a burgeoning residential neighborhood in San Francisco's South of Market district, The Folsom Lantern has two- and three-bedroom units with large windows, high ceilings, and private balconies.
Building features secure garage parking, elevator, and a common rear deck overlooking a quiet tree-lined street.
Boutique Building features 22 unique units & high-end finishes.
New In-Residence Washer/Dryer Laundry Unit Provided.
1 Car Garage Parking for additional charge of $250 per month.
Cats & Small Breed Dogs Considered with restrictions for additional deposit/fee.
